ed\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\">Ἀγάθη\u003C/span>\u003C/span> χρησ-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>τιανὴ μαίῳ \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>μηνὶ τς ε´ \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>εἰσβατό[ς] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/8ENX9UZ5\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/8ENX9UZ5\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>𐆠\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΕΤΕΛΕΥΤΗΣΕ[.]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\">ΑΓΑΘΗ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΧΡΗΣ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΤΙΑΝΗΜΑΙΩ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΜΗΝΙΤΣΕ\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ΕΙΣΒΑΤΟ[.]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003626_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2015-01-13\" src=\"ISic003626_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003626.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2015-01-13\" src=\"ISic003626-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>((Staurogram)) Agathe, a Christian, passed away the fifth day of May, accessible\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>It is unclear what the final word might signify, whether it is meant to indicate something like 'welcoming' (so Orsi), or instead to indicate that further burials are permitted in the loculus (so Rizzone). Ferrua proposed reading εἰς βᾶκε, i.e. 'in pace', 'in peace'.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Orsi 1934 151-152 no.3 fig.22 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001697\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001697\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Orsi 1942 225-226 tav.17 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001696\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001696\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1943-1944 98-99 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002000\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002000\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rizzone 2009 55-56 no.5 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001633\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001633\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Alpha tending to cursive, epsilon quadrate with equal bars, sigma lunate of quadrate form, theta ovoid with full cross-bar.\u003C/p> Line 1-6  25  Inter